## Limitations

This report is based on available data up to October 2023 and may not account for the most recent developments in the global oil market. Additionally, the complexity of global supply chains and geopolitical factors means that predictions about future price movements are inherently uncertain. The report relies on secondary sources, which may have their own biases and limitations.

